The,RIOJA,Repository,Interface,for,Overlaid,Journal,Archives,Journal,Repository,API,acts,as,an,interface,between,digital,repositories,of,articles,and,overlay,journals,Overlay,journals,are,journals,that,draw,on,one,or,more,archives,or,repositories,for,their,articles,This,API,provides,XML,based,methods,of,retrieving,information,from,journals,and,repositories,that,facilitate,the,creation,and,maintenance,of,overlay,journals